OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782188270
OL,3,CBritain to have surplus of energy for
OL,4,Cwinter despite Iran war, forecasts show
OL,6,FBritain has more than enough
OL,7,Felectricity supply to meet demand
OL,8,Fthrough the winter months, despite
OL,9,Fhouseholds facing higher bills
OL,10,Ffollowing the Iran war, according to
OL,11,Fthe energy system operator.
OL,13,FThe National Energy System Operator
OL,14,F(Neso) nonetheless cautioned over
OL,15,F"tight days" during potential cold
OL,16,Fsnaps this winter.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
