FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782188270
OL,3,CBritain to have surplus of energy for
OL,4,Cwinter despite Iran war, forecasts show
OL,6,FIn its early winter outlook, the
OL,7,Felectricity system is forecast to have
OL,8,Fa surplus of 5.5 gigawatts (GW)
OL,9,Fbetween the end of October and the end
OL,10,Fof March next year.
OL,12,FThis represents an 8.8% buffer of peak
OL,13,Fwinter demand, which is slightly below
OL,14,Fthe margin forecast for 2025, but
OL,15,Fgreater than the years before that.
OL,17,FNeso, which is a publicly-owned body,
OL,18,Findependent of government, is tasked
OL,19,Fwith ensuring that the supply of
OL,20,Felectricity remains balanced with
OL,21,Fdemand for it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782188270
OL,3,CBritain to have surplus of energy for
OL,4,Cwinter despite Iran war, forecasts show
OL,6,FIf supply cannot meet demand, then the
OL,7,Fcountry risks blackouts.
OL,9,FNeso said its modelling ` which stress-
OL,10,Ftests thousands of scenarios based on
OL,11,Felectricity demand, weather conditions
OL,12,Fand generation ` shows that Britain's
OL,13,Felectricity system is expected to
OL,14,Fremain stable this winter.
OL,16,FDespite the recent energy shock from
OL,17,Fthe Iran war, reserves are expected to
OL,18,Fbe higher than during the 2022 energy
OL,19,Fcrisis, when there was a smaller
OL,20,Fsurplus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782188270
OL,3,CBritain to have surplus of energy for
OL,4,Cwinter despite Iran war, forecasts show
OL,6,FThis is because the UK gets most of
OL,7,Fits liquified natural gas (LNG) from
OL,8,Fthe US and little comes from the
OL,9,FMiddle East, while Britain also gets
OL,10,Fenergy supplies from the North Sea and
OL,11,Frenewable sources like wind generation
OL,12,Fand solar power.
OL,14,FIncreased battery storage capacity and
OL,15,Fnew gas-fired power generation is also
OL,16,Fexpected to help meet peaks in demand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
