PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782188270
OL,3,CBritain to have surplus of energy for
OL,4,Cwinter despite Iran war, forecasts show
OL,6,FHowever, gas prices for winter and
OL,7,Fmore volatile than in recent years
OL,8,Ffollowing the conflict in the Middle
OL,9,FEast and the effective closure of the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz, a key international
OL,11,Ftransit route, Neso said.
OL,13,FThis means that the main impact of the
OL,14,Fcrisis will be felt in household
OL,15,Fbills, with Ofgem's energy price cap
OL,16,Frising by 13% from July 1.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
