OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782188270
OL,3,CBritain to have surplus of energy for
OL,4,Cwinter despite Iran war, forecasts show
OL,6,FHigher prices could mean that some
OL,7,Fhouseholds use less electricity to
OL,8,Fcombat bigger bills, which was seen
OL,9,Fafter the 2022 energy crisis following
OL,10,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine, but this
OL,11,Fis not currently being forecast.
OL,13,FNeso instead cautioned over the
OL,14,Fpotential for "tight days" where
OL,15,Fdemand for energy is high,
OL,16,Fparticularly during cold days when
OL,17,Fmore people want to heat their homes.
OL,26,@vD@OOUvD@ZO]
