PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782188270
OL,3,CBritain to have surplus of energy for
OL,4,Cwinter despite Iran war, forecasts show
OL,6,FThis could require the use of system
OL,7,Fnotices, which are how the grid
OL,8,Foperator informs the wider energy
OL,9,Findustry that electricity supply has
OL,10,Fnot matched demand, allowing for
OL,11,Fproduction to increase if needed.
OL,13,FEarly data suggest that these days are
OL,14,Fmost likely to occur in mid- to late-
OL,15,FJanuary 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
