OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782188270
OL,3,CBritain to have surplus of energy for
OL,4,Cwinter despite Iran war, forecasts show
OL,6,FDeborah Petterson, director of whole
OL,7,Fenergy system resilience at Neso,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This has been a year of
OL,9,Fturbulence in energy markets and
OL,10,Fgeopolitical uncertainty, however
OL,11,FGreat Britain's electricity system has
OL,12,Fa strong track record of reliability.
OL,14,F"This early view shows a positive
OL,15,Fpicture for the months ahead, with
OL,16,Fsufficient electricity margins
OL,17,Fexpected throughout winter.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
