OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782188270
OL,3,CBritain to have surplus of energy for
OL,4,Cwinter despite Iran war, forecasts show
OL,6,F"While we will continue to monitor
OL,7,Fglobal energy markets, households and
OL,8,Fbusinesses can be confident that
OL,9,Felectricity supplies remain secure."
